Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US-USSR nuclear deal kept quiet
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99ns
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 May 1976
President Ford keeps US-USSR nuclear pact quiet. Suggestion that Ford is concerned about being seen as weak on foreign policy. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less